These files are for drafting a U.S. Patent Application using LaTeX or LyX.

src/

	patentex.cls - LaTeX class file based on memoir
	genfig       - bash script to create figure based on tikz file

demo/
	PatApp.tex   - Sample patent application


+++++++++++++++++++
INSTALL INFORMATION
+++++++++++++++++++

To allow LaTeX to find the patentex class file, ADD the following
line to your .bashrc file:

  export TEXINPUTS="<PATH TO DIRECTORY CONTAINING patentex.cls>:"

NOTE:  Make sure you include the ending colon.
